00:13:23.515 --> 00:13:25.568
ver veyst, me ken tsuganvenen."

00:13:26.569 --> 00:13:28.098
ikh hob oysgeton.

00:13:28.695 --> 00:13:32.114
der iker, bay nakht hot genumen geyn a regn a mabl.

00:13:32.526 --> 00:13:35.355
vi zikh onton di, di shtivelekh, nito

00:13:36.593 --> 00:13:40.007
di goye vos lebn ir khate bay ir oyfn hoyf shlofn mir, hot zi geganvet

00:13:40.007 --> 00:13:42.251
zi gemeynt zi vet do gefinen goldene imperyal.

00:13:42.251 --> 00:13:44.056
keyn goldene hot zi nit gefunen

00:13:44.056 --> 00:13:47.094
nor kloles hobn mir ir gegebn genug vos zi hot tsugenumen.

00:13:47.094 --> 00:13:49.693
der iker, un ikh ken gornit WALKen borves

00:13:49.693 --> 00:13:52.891
hot der man mir opgegebn zaynen shikh. s'iz geven tsu groys

00:13:52.891 --> 00:13:54.980
UNK fun ayere a por shikh ken ikh geyn

00:13:55.037 --> 00:13:56.685
un er iz gegangen borves.

00:13:56.809 --> 00:13:58.018
hert zikh ayn.

00:13:58.193 --> 00:14:01.039
nu, un mir heybn on geyn itster oyf Grodne.

00:14:01.534 --> 00:14:04.281
mir, es fort durkh a GRUZOVIK, a TRUCK

00:14:04.281 --> 00:14:07.144
nemt er undz aroyf, ober ⟨aza vald avegn⟩ gor links

00:14:07.144 --> 00:14:08.784
un mir darfn geyn mit dem ROAD

00:14:08.784 --> 00:14:10.454
vos oyf Grodne geyen mir

00:14:10.461 --> 00:14:13.458
a- un mir geyen arayn betn broyt. me git undz

00:14:13.515 --> 00:14:16.880
un ot azoy geyen mir. bay tog geyen mir, un bay nakht

