leygn mir zikh avek

00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:19.030
in, in a vald

00:14:19.030 --> 00:14:21.270
lebn br- nit vayt fun ROAD shlofn.

00:14:21.632 --> 00:14:24.359
mir geyen, mir geyen. mir zaynen shoyn mistome a

00:14:24.619 --> 00:14:25.777
kh'veys a

00:14:25.817 --> 00:14:28.522
fuftsik kilometer tsi fertsik

00:14:28.522 --> 00:14:29.676
fun Grodne

00:14:30.407 --> 00:14:31.734
iz

00:14:31.909 --> 00:14:35.041
hobn mir geshlofn in a shtetl, Vasilishok

00:14:35.250 --> 00:14:36.006
iz ge-

00:14:36.006 --> 00:14:36.982
neyn, neyn

00:14:37.849 --> 00:14:40.090
nit in Vasilishok. s'iz geven in an ander ort

00:14:40.090 --> 00:14:43.496
iz a, a daytsh- a rusisher koronel

00:14:43.536 --> 00:14:44.781
iz gekumen

