00:16:50.672 --> 00:16:54.474
"vestu hobn a gute shtele," un ⟨di⟩ milkhome geyt nokh on, fir un fertsik

00:16:54.474 --> 00:16:58.091
"vet men dir nit DRAFTn in der milkhome, vayl Berlin darf men dokh nokh farnemen."

00:16:58.738 --> 00:17:02.507
may- UNK gekumen in shtub. mir hobn glaykh ongeshribn a PETITION

00:17:02.507 --> 00:17:05.601
avek in N.K.V.D., dos zey gegebn. m'hot im glaykh arayngenumen.

00:17:06.012 --> 00:17:09.679
m'hot im arayngenumen in, in, in tyurme hot er gearbet.

00:17:09.679 --> 00:17:11.000
freyer in arkhiv

00:17:11.142 --> 00:17:13.248
mit dokumentn, nakher in tyurme.

00:17:13.248 --> 00:17:15.556
un do heybt men on itster shlepn polyakn

00:17:15.968 --> 00:17:18.341
vos zaynen geven, vos zey hobn gedint dem daytsh.

00:17:18.786 --> 00:17:19.488
nu

00:17:19.545 --> 00:17:21.361
un ot azoy iz dos UNK.

00:17:19.900 --> 00:17:21.294
ir hot gez-

00:17:21.637 --> 00:17:24.500
ah antshuldikt, ir hot gezukht ayer mishpokhe?

00:17:24.590 --> 00:17:28.268
zikher. un az keyner iz nito akht monatn hob ikh gevart in Grodne.

00:17:28.268 --> 00:17:30.948
efsher UNK es hobn zikh umgekert andere fun AUSCHWITZ.

00:17:30.970 --> 00:17:34.519
zey hobn, az zey hobn beshas m'hot aroysgefirt di letste fun AUSCHWITZ

00:17:34.519 --> 00:17:37.480
hobn zey on a zayt zikh gekent araynganvenen in vald

00:17:37.480 --> 00:17:39.092
un zey hobn gekumen in Grodne.

00:17:39.092 --> 00:17:42.878
hobn zey dertseylt vos do iz, az m'hot fargazt, az m'hot farbrent.

00:17:42.411 --> 00:17:46.607
un z- vos iz geven der sof fun ayer tate un ayer shvester?

00:17:46.005 --> 00:17:48.238
veys ikh n- di mame iz ⟨do⟩ geshtorbn in geto.

00:17:48.238 --> 00:17:51.984
der foter hot men genumen mitn, mitn tsveyte oyszidlung fun

00:17:51.984 --> 00:17:53.710
fun Slabodker geto.

00:17:54.696 --> 00:17:55.950
vi ikh gleyb

00:17:55.950 --> 00:17:59.392
keyner iz nit geblibn lebn fun der, dem transport.

00:17:59.392 --> 00:18:02.906
az er hot nit derforn, er hot afile AUSCHWITZ nit gezen far di oygn

00:18:02.906 --> 00:18:04.656
er iz in vagon dershtikt gevorn.

00:18:04.656 --> 00:18:06.252
dos iz geven vagones fun

00:18:06.252 --> 00:18:07.161
CATTLE.

00:18:07.318 --> 00:18:09.236
nit keyn pasazhir vagonen

00:18:09.512 --> 00:18:12.898
un men hot ⟨dos⟩ gefirt, un di engshaft iz geven groys

00:18:13.883 --> 00:18:15.142
s- er iz zikher

00:18:13.883 --> 00:18:16.087
un d- un di shvester?

00:18:15.975 --> 00:18:18.410
mayn shvester hot men shpeter aroysgefirt.

00:18:18.410 --> 00:18:22.823
vos m'hot gezogt az ikh bin a meshugene vos ikh gey aroys vinter loyf ikh aroys fun geto.

00:18:22.823 --> 00:18:24.156
un zi iz nokh geblibn

00:18:24.156 --> 00:18:27.258
ir hot men aroysgefirt, dem transport hot men gefirt in TREBLINKA.

00:18:27.990 --> 00:18:28.847
veys ikh.

00:18:28.847 --> 00:18:30.346
mer veys ikh gornit.

00:18:28.986 --> 00:18:31.865
mit ir, mit ir man, mit kinder?

00:18:31.922 --> 00:18:35.341
a- ale, ale avek in TREBLINKA.

00:18:35.871 --> 00:18:37.080
itster

00:18:37.761 --> 00:18:40.067
vos no- akht monatn hob ikh gevart

00:18:40.461 --> 00:18:41.923
un

00:18:42.081 --> 00:18:44.938
itster hob ikh bashlosn aroysforn

00:18:44.938 --> 00:18:49.533
Poyln. nokh Grodne iz Byalistok. tsvishn Grodne un Byalistok iz der grenets.

00:18:50.265 --> 00:18:53.819
Grodne iz geven Rusland, un Byalistok iz Poyln.

00:18:54.805 --> 00:18:58.327
ober s'iz alts geven in der emesn iz geven alts UNK a FICTION geven.

00:18:58.327 --> 00:19:00.097
in der emesn dos alts balangt tsu Rusland.

00:19:00.097 --> 00:19:02.724
nor UNK gemakht a poylishn GOVERNMENT.

00:19:02.724 --> 00:19:04.872
poylish iz geven di ADMINISTRATION.

00:19:05.098 --> 00:19:08.990
kum ikh tsurik, kum ikh m- far peysekh kumen mir in Byalistok.

00:19:09.317 --> 00:19:10.790
⟨iz shoyn⟩ der JOINT

00:19:10.790 --> 00:19:13.254
der JOINT DISTRIBUTION hot shoyn gearbet

00:19:13.254 --> 00:19:17.496
hobn mir gekrogn vayn un matse, matse mel oyf makhn k- kneydlekh.

00:19:17.518 --> 00:19:20.229
m'hot shoyn gekrogn esn peysekhdike.

00:19:20.033 --> 00:19:22.524
ir gedenkt dem sof fun di milkhome?

00:19:22.564 --> 00:19:25.033
vo- i- UNK voynen mir, ot vel ikh geyn

